<subSubSection pageId="793" pageNumber="794" type="diversity">
<paragraph pageId="793" pageNumber="794">Diversity.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="793" pageNumber="794">About 45 species in temperate, subtropical, and tropical areas of the Western Hemisphere arrayed in 11 species groups. Five species are found in North America.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
